        en: 'The UAE offers a unique experience: in Dubai and Abu Dhabi you join international campuses of leading British, American and Australian universities, in a safe, ultra-modern Muslim country. English teaching, global economic hubs, proximity to companies for internships and jobs. Ideal for an international career in business, engineering, hospitality, finance or tech.'),
